I want to tell about my last ten years what I experienced about my life 
Firstly, my daughter was born in Aksaray in 2010 and nowadays she is eleven. her name is Şevval and she studies in secondary school.

Secondly, while I was working at Aksaray Public hospital, I was dismissed from my profession in 2016. I was at prison for a year. I started to learn English by myself over there. I wanted to improve myself about English. 

After that, I started to work at the private INOVA hospital two years ago. I still work there. 
I have started a course to learn English for a month. Because I want to go abroad with my family. I would like to keep living in England from now on  

























